<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Scrabble World Champions — Complete History & Records</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Since 1991, the World Scrabble Championship has crowned champions from six continents. These players represent the absolute pinnacle of word knowledge, board strategy, and mental endurance. No player has ever won twice — a testament to how brutally competitive the field has become.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Championship Overview</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">1991</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">First WSC held</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">20+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Countries represented</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">0</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Repeat winners</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Notable World Champions</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
  <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
    <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <tr>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Year</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Champion</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Country</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Notable</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">1991</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Peter Morris</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇺🇸 USA</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Inaugural champion</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">1993</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Mark Nyman</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇬🇧 UK</td><td class="px-4 py-3">British dominance era</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">1999</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Joel Sherman</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇺🇸 USA</td><td class="px-4 py-3">"G.I. Joel" — legendary nickname</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">2003</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Panupol Sujjayakorn</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇹🇭 Thailand</td><td class="px-4 py-3">First Asian champion</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">2007</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Nigel Richards</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇳🇿 New Zealand</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Greatest player ever</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">2015</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Craig Beevers</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇬🇧 UK</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Recent British champion</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">2019</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Wellington Jighere</td><td class="px-4 py-3">🇳🇬 Nigeria</td><td class="px-4 py-3">First African champion</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Legend of Nigel Richards</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Greatest of All Time</div>
  <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">NIGEL RICHARDS</p>
  <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">Multiple WSC wins · French champion (without speaking French) · Unmatched dominance</p>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Nigel Richards is widely considered the greatest Scrabble player of all time. He memorised the entire French Scrabble dictionary — without speaking French — and won the Francophone World Championship. His board vision, anagram speed, and strategic depth remain unrivalled in competitive history.</p>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">What Makes a World Champion</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">📖 Word Knowledge</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Champions know 170,000+ valid words. Most memorise the entire SOWPODS dictionary including obscure 2-letter words and 8-letter bingos.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
    <p class="text-purple-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">🧠 Anagram Speed</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Top players can anagram any 7-letter rack in under 3 seconds. This speed allows them to evaluate 5+ play options per turn within time limits.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
    <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">♟️ Board Strategy</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Knowing when to open vs close the board, blocking triple-word lanes, and managing tile distribution are as important as word knowledge.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
    <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">🏋️ Mental Endurance</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">WSC involves 30+ games over several days. Champions maintain focus, accuracy, and strategic sharpness across marathon tournament schedules.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 bg-indigo-950/10">
